'''Skeletons''' are found in [[Tarn's Lair]]. They have the same appearance as [[Skeleton Mage]]s, and also share the same stat-reducing attack which reduces [[Attack]], [[Strength]] and [[Defence]] stats by 3-4 levels, exclaiming "I infect your body with rot...". They are able to recognize the player's [[protection prayers]] and will switch attack styles accordingly, although their melee attack is weaker and less accurate than their Magic attack.

Their [[Magic]] attack resembles [[Earth Bolt]] and will only be used if the player is unreachable or using protection from melee.

